    <h3>Community Information</h3>
    <p>The third largest city in Arizona, Mesa is located in the southwest region of America. With
warm weather all year, outdoor fun is alive and well. Urban fishing, golfing, dog parks, and
mountain climbing are just a few ways to pass time. Known for its art and culture, there are
museums, public art and sculptures in the streets for everyone to enjoy. Coupled with many
great restaurants and a large variety of shopping stores in a beautiful landscape, Mesa is the
perfect city to discover.</p>
