    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>With an unprecedented excellence in education, Mesa Public Schools work to establish
realistic priorities, goals and objectives for students. The largest school district in Arizona,
the district serves over 69,000 students, allowing for a great mix of people, intellect,
interests and opportunities for personal growth. With a mission to develop a highly
educated and productive community, one student at a time, each student is paid individual
attention. Understanding that each student is important, the teachers take the extra time
to make sure the material being taught is also understood. Although large, Mesa Public
Schools work hard to provide the best learning environment for their students, and in turn,
provide the best foundation for their future.</p>
